Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:20.09,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I put together dried up words...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:28.83,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but all I want to do is convey\N my simple feelings to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:34.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The faint wind that blew from that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:38.40,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I threw it away in yesterday's ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:44.55,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So I can live today with you with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:52.19,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But still, this incident will\N continue to trouble you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:57.08,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's why it must be a goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:01:04.12,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now we just try to understand\N each other until nothing remains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:11.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And eventually, we will realize\N that it was everything to us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:18.01,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Sadness will run down our cheeks,\N creating a river of tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:28.97,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,1700)}Trembling thoughts will become a strong\N whirl and melt together into one
Comment: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:30.04,OP5,,0,0,0,,OP End

Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.56,0:01:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll grant you one wish, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.77,0:01:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your strong will is going to remain\Nas Residual Aura inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:02:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you'll lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, your flesh is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, Lord Orochimaru's body\Nhas once again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,become unable to reanimate\Nfor several years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,However there's a next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I-lndeed. My body no longer has value\Nas a vessel for Reanimation Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It will now be difficult for me\Nwho has lost everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to find my own calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally understood that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's not me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring in the new "vessel,"\Neven if it costs me my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:03:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my repayment to\NLord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only redemption for me...\Nwho was worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:12.92,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(490,497)}Mistake! A New Enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistake! A New Enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Akamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come quick after you've set the bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Akamaru, well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Messing with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Akamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you "arf" me, you mutt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll waste you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiba! Akamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Kiba and Akamaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one's come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of this, so you take\Nthe coffin and go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Get going already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Naruto.\NIt's my miscalculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimimaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You were taking too long, Tayuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happened to\Nthe other three?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Being none other than those\Nof the former "Sound Ninja Five."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body... Your body's no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not moving with the flesh anymore.\NIt's mental power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you cheater of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand a little now,\Nthat feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,of being information that has escaped\Nfrom the prison of the flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The feeling of experiencing\Na taste of Lord Orochimaru's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This vessel... is an important vessel\Nfor the dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The flesh that Lord Orochimaru\Ntruly desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But you guys were a bit too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Some dangerous guy\Nhas appeared again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That air about him is\Nnothing ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we need\Nto sort out the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were to carelessly\Nplunge in...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk.\NWhat're you babbling nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Give back Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tayuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason why I won't kill you now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,is because you have a mission\Nyou have to complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And my mission is to deliver\Nthat to Lord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it too late now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph. I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the body that Lord Orochimaru\Ntruly desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The next vessel, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the only thing that\NI can do at present.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave those two pieces\Nof garbage to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I calm down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate,\NSasuke will get far away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a mission to bring Sasuke back\Nto the Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We must choose what would be\Nthe most rational means
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to execute the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned punks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish this in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please move according to the plan\Nthat I'm going to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a classic close-range\Ncombat-type fool
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,with Shadow Clone Jutsu\Nas his only saving grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's a middle-range\Ncombat type
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,who binds his enemies with\Na Jutsu using shadows...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and a sharp squad leader, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on already, you punks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's two versus one.\NWe've got the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an opponent we can beat\Nif we team up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With garbage like you jerks,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't matter how many\Nof you are there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate our teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll blow you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha. The strategy is a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You tricked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,T eamwork, my foot. You little punks...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't fall for the same trick\Nover and over, huh..?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:12:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Small fry... You've got nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll settle for just\Nhaving been able to let him get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just Jutsu that are weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But that kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,how wonderful it is that\Nhe can move with that body, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabuto, I don't know what kind\Nof order you gave him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's a bit harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.\NIt wasn't an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like to force things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He acted on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For you whom he reveres.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabuto... You've really got\Na hateful personality, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To you,\NKimimaro was a perfect existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,His thoughts were steeped in darkness\Nin the same way as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And he sanctified you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And he fanatically admired\Nand revered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, he was of the Shinobi clan\Nwith the strongest and perfect bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,being the legitimate bloodline\Nof their Kekkai Genkai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,until a short time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think about having lost him,\NI still get a chill down my spine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I think about it even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:14:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The man I truly wished for...\NThe body I wanted the most... Kimimaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And if only he hadn't been stricken\Nwith disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the assassination of the Hokage\Nwould've gone smoother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... you can no longer use\Neither of your arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And since you can't use your arms,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't weave Sign...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You no longer possess Ninjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ambition of crushing\Nthe Hidden Leaf... dies right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru, you fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unfortunate that we can't leave\Ntogether but, my disciple...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's meet in the other world\None day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...\NSasuke's not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't have needed to go\Nthrough such an experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In the world, very often things don't go\Nas we want them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time,\NLord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When Tayuya... comes back,\NI'll kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, how shall I defeat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he possesses\Na peculiar Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:17:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What does Orochimaru want to do...?\NWhy's he after Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Orochimaru has already\Nobtained lmmortality Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time is necessary to get every Jutsu\Nand obtain everything in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that have to do\Nwith Sasuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,," lmmortal" doesn't mean that\Nthe flesh is being maintained as is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Before his body decays,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,a strong and new flesh will be made\Ninto a vessel for his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that's Sasuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let such a thing happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot... What will come of sending\None shrimp punk in pursuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:18:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And looking at things\Nin terms of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,up until now you probably sacrificed\None member each time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in order for the group\Nto move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that guy called Sasuke\Nthat important?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How many of your men do you intend\Nto sacrifice for the sake of just one person?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You incompetent punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh... Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, this is my first mission\Nas a platoon leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very disquieting having\Ncomrades gradually whittled down,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't know if my own judgments\Nwere correct or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As a squad leader with\Nthe lives of the party in my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,respecting the lives in\Nthe four-member party,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than the life of one person\Ntaken by the enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:19:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and deciding to abort a mission\Nthat's too dangerous, would be by the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why didn't you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The world doesn't go\Nby the book very often...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Since not one person in my squad\Nwould do something like
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,abandon a captured comrade and give up\Nfighting for the sake of their own safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Me included.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Being the cloud-loving loafer myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not cut out to be a squad leader\Nwho gives orders to comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I can do for them...\Nis to have faith in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. I'm not thinking anything\Nlike they were sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not thinking anything\Nlike they've died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mock my comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Summoning Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't... Iook so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll play a melody of death for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you mock us,\Nyou damned punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you take Sasuke,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Comment: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:07.07,ED8,,0,0,0,,ED Start
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:15.37,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:18.46,ED8,,0,0,0,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:21.00,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:23.80,ED8,,0,0,0,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:29.44,ED8,,0,0,0,,Would you think it was\Na bother if I approached you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:34.85,ED8,,0,0,0,,Despite my doubts,\NI worked up my courage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:40.78,ED8,,0,0,0,,My clumsy attempts with words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:46.45,ED8,,0,0,0,,You listened without turning away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:52.57,ED8,,0,0,0,,No wonder I get carried away by you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:59.64,ED8,,0,0,0,,But you don't feel anything for me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:02.84,ED8,,0,0,0,,I feel so sad
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:03.81,ED8,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.81,0:22:06.28,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.28,0:22:09.32,ED8,,0,0,0,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.32,0:22:12.05,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.05,0:22:15.12,ED8,,0,0,0,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.12,0:22:17.63,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.63,0:22:20.83,ED8,,0,0,0,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.83,0:22:23.37,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:26.34,ED8,,0,0,0,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:30.97,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I spoke to you
